---
description: Next.js and React conventions
globs: "**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use App Router patterns (`app/` directory, layouts, loading states)
- Prefer `fetch` with Next.js caching conventions over ad-hoc data fetching
- Use TypeScript strict mode — no `any` unless unavoidable
- Match existing component and file naming in the repo
